caller_intent: Jeff Edmonds is contacting Casey to correct a spelling error in the middle name of a minor on a bond previously issued by Alliance Insurance Services.
resolution_steps: Casey asks for the bond number and details of the error.
Jeff provides the bond number (CBE1065414) and clarifies the middle name should be 'NOELLE' instead of the current spelling.
Casey confirms the correction and requests Jeff's email address for sending the updated information.
Jeff provides his email (jeff@allianceinsurance.com), and Casey agrees to send the correction immediately.
knowledge_required: Understanding how to access and modify bond records
Knowledge of proper email communication for document corrections
summary: Jeff Edmonds contacted Casey to correct a spelling error in a minor's middle name on a bond. Casey confirmed the bond details, requested the corrected spelling, and agreed to send the updated information via email. The call concluded with Casey taking action to resolve the issue.
